35:14.112 --> 35:16.897
I guess I'm still a little
peeved that you both blamed me

35:16.940 --> 35:18.594
for not handling
the dad news perfectly.

35:18.638 --> 35:20.640
And I am sorry
if I said something

35:20.683 --> 35:22.207
that hurt you.Okay.

35:22.250 --> 35:24.383
Maggie?Oh, I unpacked with
Lucy. I'm cool.

35:24.426 --> 35:26.036
Oh.

35:26.080 --> 35:27.690
ALL:
Tonde daimon amauroun,

35:27.734 --> 35:29.953
hos tane psychane hairein!

